        </div>
      <br>
      <p class= "para">Plaza Mayor is where you can do some shopping, eat authentic food, stop at a cafe and enjoy everything the outdoors brings you. Plaza Mayor is at the center of Madrid and was first built in 1580-1619 so there is a historic feel to this outdoor public area. As a tourist, some things you may see in this public area are children playing soccer and many people enjoying a coffee at the local cafe. This is also the center where many concerts are performed and festivals are happening throughout the year.</p>
