        </div>
        <br>
        <p class= "para">This is the palace where many Royal Spanish families reside; however, the current royal family lives just outside Madrid in a more functional palace. The Royal Palace of Madrid is currently where many ceremonies take place involving the royal family and government of Madrid. This palace is massive. It is a long walk to take from one side of the palace to the other so make sure to wear the proper shoes for walking while exploring this area of Madrid. It is definitely worth the walk when you get to see the palace. Its architecture is beautiful and it has fine details such as the gold that surrounds the building.</p>
