          <p class= "para">If you enjoy shopping, good food, and movies the Gran Via is the perfect place for you. Gran Via is Madrid’s center for shopping. It is a long street that starts at Calle de Alcalá and ends at  Plaza de España. Along with shopping be sure to stop to see the famous symbol of Madrid the bear and the strawberry tree which is just a six-minute walk from Calle Gran Via.</p>
